file_content.text: So you stumbled across our little operation? Too bad you won't live long enough to tell anyone about our plans!
I surrender my spirit to Tyth...
I know you, Outlander! I wonder if the legends are true? Can you survive against an entire Zakuulan battalion?
Second wave--we fight for the glory of Zakuul!
Reinforcements! Destroy the enemies of the Eternal Empire!
Impressive... but now you must face a real challenge!
Annihilate our foes. Hold nothing back!
I serve the Eternal Empire... I cannot... die.
